A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a person sitting at a mid-century modern desk, carefully placing manila folders into an ornate wooden filing cabinet with multiple brass-handled drawers. The scene shows a warm amber-tinted office with organized stacks of documents, a rotary phone, and sunlight streaming through venetian blinds casting striped shadows. The filing cabinet drawers are arranged in a cascading open pattern, revealing color-coded folders being sorted with precision. A satisfied expression on the person's face suggests the joy of organization. The overall palette features warm sepia tones, cream, burnt orange, and forest green, evoking a nostalgic sense of order and efficiency from a bygone era.
